{"tid":1761921,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人依家應該點做","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T08:52:54.000Z","uid":321381,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ba3715e43e13c4c13c49925924f55d9d7a463e","tid":1761921,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉贏左，民主人權法案通過左。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭必需要持續，救香港的仍然是香港人。<br />\n<br />\n問題是系在法案buff嘅加持，全世界都焦點香港下，香港人有咩選擇可做。普天同慶似乎唔系一個好選擇。<br />\n<br />\n記住，buff 系有時限嫁，即使法案通過，特朗普系可以咩都唔做，系因為民意，所以先咁快過，我地系到打飛機，普天同慶，比美國人以為搞掂左，咪晒消氣冇晒民意囉。唔止系美國，依家區選贏左一樣系咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家其實要做嘅系，如果法案真系有用嘅話，我可以利用基本法比我地遊行，集會，罷工嘅權利，形成更大嘅聲音，比壓力政府，比全世界知依個系香港六成人都支持嘅五大訴求。比美國人知道我地仲未光復到，革命尚未成功。<br />\n<br />\n見唔到林鄭龜縮晒咩，因為時不與她，但時正與我們!!!!<br />\n<br />\n見唔到中央搵解放軍出聲嚇大家咩，正因為依家最唔出得兵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡單泥講</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攞住果勢</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食住上</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行、集會、罷工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞大佢</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有風駛盡佢</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Now or never</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n沉寃待雪<br />\n<br />\n香港人，堅持"},{"pid":"c8761580e91a77eed54f59be48a40c9b4525116b","tid":1761921,"uid":30146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"721 831 101 1111 1118"},{"pid":"b8bdec5e632d6460d4f085f11f106fab5063a